caption: I haven't been in the Jack & Jack fandom for over a year, but I support them and love them as much as anyone else. Jack & Jack, you have gave me confidence, which is something I've been struggling with for years. Thank You for getting me out of my shell. I'd like to meet you so I could thank you in person and maybe even get hug from you guys. Even if I don't win this #contest , I will still support you and try to meet you every time you come to Dallas, TX ???❤️ I'll probably be that old lady at Starbucks who's listening to your music and favoriting your tweets ? Congratulations to the fan who wins this #contest , and hopefully it could be me ❤️?
